Reinforce in educating the community on what is provided in NSWMC in compliance with RA No. 9003; and
Take appropriate action in making efficient use of the different facilities and equipment expended by the agency.

1.) Create an inventory committee to conduct a physical count of the properties of the municipality and submit the Inventory Report to the Municipal Accountant and to the Office of the Auditor; 
