3.) Municipal Accountant and GSO/Municipal Treasurer maintain ledgers and stock and property cards, respectively. Also, maintain a Property, Plant and Equipment Register to facilitate the conduct of year-end physical inventory, and as basis in the conduct and reconciliation of the accounts; and 
